ygData.messageBody:
After compiling a list of all songs available, including those in HighPass
Hold Keep and Erudin, I am still missing 30, 38, 39, 43-50th level songs.

Has anyone seen a bard vendor from another city other than Freeport,
Highpass Keep, Kelethin, Qeynos, and Erudin?

I would be highly interested to recieve this information ASAP.
They have to be out there somewhere.

Nyxa Mederio <Krieger>
Half Dark Elf Bardess of Veeshan on Tunare
